videos.description: Asim Rose Jr. says the Kentucky seniors just wanted to go out with a win after he rushes for a career-high 148 yards against Indiana.
videos.headline: UK's Rose Jr. blossoms with MVP effort in Gator Bowl

videos.description: UK's Mark Stoops says the Gator Bowl win over Indiana is in honor of the late John Schlarman and the ailing Chris Oates.
videos.headline: Stoops dedicates Kentucky win to Schlarman, Oates

videos.description: Kentucky uses a punishing 281-yard rushing attack and an opportunistic defense to upset No. 23 North Carolina State.
videos.headline: UK grinds out 23-21 Gator Bowl win over N.C. State
